  "questions": [
    {
      "id": "c2-I-1",
      "number": "I-1",
      "topic": "二次函数在区间上的最值（含参）",
      "topicTag": "二次函数",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$f(x) = x^2 - 2(a+1)x + 2a^2$，$0 \\le x \\le 2$ 上的最大值 $M$、最小值 $m$（$0 \\le a \\le 3$）。\n\n(1) 顶点 $(a + \\fbox{A}, a^2 - \\fbox{B}\\,a - \\fbox{C})$。\n\n(2) $0 \\le a < \\fbox{D}$：$M = \\fbox{E}, m = \\fbox{F}$；$\\fbox{D} \\le a \\le 3$：$M = \\fbox{G}, m = \\fbox{H}$。\n选项：⓪ $0$ ① $1$ ② $2$ ③ $3$ ④ $a^2 - 2a$ ⑤ $a^2 - 2a - 1$ ⑥ $2a^2$ ⑦ $2a^2 - 2a - 1$ ⑧ $2a^2 - 4a$ ⑨ $2a^2 - 6a + 3$\n\n(3) $m$ 最大在 $a = \\fbox{I}$，值为 $\\fbox{J}$；$m$ 最小在 $a = \\fbox{K}$，值为 $\\fbox{LM}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "$f(x) = (x - (a+1))^2 - (a+1)^2 + 2a^2 = (x-(a+1))^2 + a^2 - 2a - 1$。",
        "analysis": "轴 $x = a + 1 \\in [1, 4]$。当轴在 $[0,2]$ 内（$a \\in [0,1]$）顶点处取最小；轴在区间右侧（$a \\ge 1$）函数在 $[0,2]$ 单调递减。最大值在远端，即 $x=0$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 顶点",
            "content": "$f(x) = (x-(a+1))^2 + 2a^2 - (a+1)^2 = (x - (a+1))^2 + a^2 - 2a - 1$。\n\n顶点 $(a+1, a^2 - 2a - 1)$。$\\fbox{A}=1, \\fbox{B}=2, \\fbox{C}=1$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 按 $a$ 分情况",
            "content": "$f(0) = 2a^2, f(2) = 4 - 4(a+1) + 2a^2 = 2a^2 - 4a$。距轴：$|0 - (a+1)| = a+1$，$|2 - (a+1)| = |1-a|$。\n\n**$0 \\le a < 1$**：轴 $a+1 \\in [1, 2)$ 在区间内。最小 $= a^2 - 2a - 1$（顶点）。$a + 1 \\ge |1-a|$，最大在 $x = 0$：$M = 2a^2$。$\\fbox{D}=1, \\fbox{E}=⑥(2a^2), \\fbox{F}=⑤(a^2-2a-1)$。\n\n**$1 \\le a \\le 3$**：轴 $\\ge 2$ 在区间右外，$f$ 在 $[0,2]$ 递减。最大 $f(0) = 2a^2$，最小 $f(2) = 2a^2 - 4a$。$\\fbox{G}=⑥(2a^2), \\fbox{H}=⑧(2a^2-4a)$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) $m$ 极值",
            "content": "$0 \\le a < 1$ 时 $m(a) = a^2 - 2a - 1$，$m'(a) = 2a - 2 < 0$ 递减。\n$1 \\le a \\le 3$ 时 $m(a) = 2a^2 - 4a$，$m'(a) = 4a - 4 \\ge 0$ 递增。\n\n所以 $m$ 在 $a=1$ 处取最小：$m(1) = 1 - 2 - 1 = -2$（或 $2 - 4 = -2$）。$\\fbox{K}=1, \\fbox{LM}=-2$。\n\n端点比较：$m(0) = -1$；$m(3) = 18 - 12 = 6$。最大在 $a = 3$：$m = 6$。$\\fbox{I}=3, \\fbox{J}=6$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "ABC=121, D=1, E=6, F=5, G=6, H=8, I=3, J=6, K=1, LM=-2"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-I-2",
      "number": "I-2",
      "topic": "骰子三次掷出与二次函数实数解",
      "topicTag": "概率·二次方程",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "骰子掷 $3$ 次得 $a, b, c$（$1\\sim6$）。$f(x) = ax^2 + bx + c$。\n\n(1) $b = 4$ 且 $f(x) = 0$ 有 $2$ 个不同实数解的概率 $= \\dfrac{\\fbox{N}}{\\fbox{OPQ}}$。\n\n(2) $f(10) > 453$ 的 $(a,b,c)$ 个数：\n  - $a=4, b=5$：$\\fbox{R}$ 通\n  - $a=4, b=6$：$\\fbox{S}$ 通\n  - $a=5$：$\\fbox{TU}$ 通\n  - $a=6$：$\\fbox{VW}$ 通\n\n概率 $= \\dfrac{\\fbox{X}}{\\fbox{Y}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "(1) 判别式 $16 - 4ac > 0 \\Rightarrow ac < 4$；(2) 枚举 $f(10) = 100a + 10b + c > 453$。",
        "analysis": "总情形 $6^3 = 216$。$ac < 4$ 的 $(a,c)$：$(1,1),(1,2),(1,3),(2,1),(3,1)$ 共 $5$ 组。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 概率",
            "content": "$b = 4$ 固定，$ac < 4$ 共 $5$ 通。总 $6^3 = 216$。概率 $= 5/216$。$\\fbox{N}=5, \\fbox{OPQ}=216$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 枚举",
            "content": "$100a + 10b + c > 453$。\n\n$a \\le 3$：$300+10b+c \\le 300 + 66 = 366 < 453$，不行。\n\n$a=4$：$10b + c > 53$。$b=1\\sim4$：$10b+c \\le 46 < 54$，不行。$b=5$：$50+c > 53 \\Rightarrow c \\in \\{4,5,6\\}$，$3$ 通。$b=6$：$60+c > 53$ 总成立，$6$ 通。$\\fbox{R}=3, \\fbox{S}=6$。\n\n$a=5$：$500+10b+c > 453$ 总成立，$6 \\cdot 6 = 36$ 通。$\\fbox{TU}=36$。\n\n$a=6$：同样 $36$ 通。$\\fbox{VW}=36$。\n\n合 $3 + 6 + 36 + 36 = 81$。概率 $= 81/216 = 3/8$。$\\fbox{X}=3, \\fbox{Y}=8$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "NOPQ=5216, R=3, S=6, TU=36, VW=36, XY=38"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-II-1",
      "number": "II-1",
      "topic": "数列通项与无穷级数",
      "topicTag": "数列·级数",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$a_1 = \\dfrac{2}{9}$，$a_n = \\dfrac{(n+1)(2n-3)}{3n(2n+1)} a_{n-1}$（$n \\ge 2$）。\n\n(1) $b_n = \\dfrac{n+1}{3^n a_n}$。$\\dfrac{b_n}{b_{n-1}} = \\dfrac{\\fbox{A}}{\\fbox{B}} \\cdot \\dfrac{a_{n-1}}{a_n} = \\dfrac{\\fbox{C}}{\\fbox{D}}$。故 $a_n = \\dfrac{n+1}{3^n(\\fbox{E})(2n+1)}$。\n选项：⓪ $n-1$ ① $n$ ② $n+1$ ③ $2n-1$ ④ $2n+1$ ⑤ $2n-3$ ⑥ $2n+3$ ⑦ $3n-1$ ⑧ $3n$ ⑨ $3n+1$\n\n(2) $c_n = \\dfrac{1}{3^n(2n+1)}$。$a_n = A c_{n-1} + B c_n$，$A = \\dfrac{\\fbox{F}}{\\fbox{G}}$，$B = \\dfrac{\\fbox{HI}}{\\fbox{J}}$。\n\n$S_n = \\dfrac{\\fbox{K}}{\\fbox{L}}(\\fbox{M} - c_n)$。$\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} a_n = \\dfrac{\\fbox{N}}{\\fbox{O}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "(1) 用 $b_n$ 比值消去 $a_n$ 关系；(2) 部分分式拆解后裂项求和。",
        "analysis": "$b_n/b_{n-1} = (n+1)/(3n) \\cdot a_{n-1}/a_n = (n+1)(2n+1)/(n(2n-3)) \\cdot 1/3 \\cdot \\ldots$ 直接计算得 $(2n+1)/(2n-3)$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) $b_n$ 比值与 $a_n$",
            "content": "$\\dfrac{b_n}{b_{n-1}} = \\dfrac{(n+1)/(3^n a_n)}{n/(3^{n-1} a_{n-1})} = \\dfrac{n+1}{3n} \\cdot \\dfrac{a_{n-1}}{a_n}$。$\\fbox{A}=②(n+1), \\fbox{B}=⑧(3n)$。\n\n$\\dfrac{a_{n-1}}{a_n} = \\dfrac{3n(2n+1)}{(n+1)(2n-3)}$，故 $\\dfrac{b_n}{b_{n-1}} = \\dfrac{2n+1}{2n-3}$。$\\fbox{C}=④(2n+1), \\fbox{D}=⑤(2n-3)$。\n\n$b_1 = 2/(3 \\cdot 2/9) = 3$。$b_n = 3 \\cdot \\prod_{k=2}^n \\dfrac{2k+1}{2k-3} = 3 \\cdot \\dfrac{(2n-1)(2n+1)}{1 \\cdot 3} = (2n-1)(2n+1)$。\n\n所以 $a_n = \\dfrac{n+1}{3^n(2n-1)(2n+1)}$。$\\fbox{E}=③(2n-1)$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 部分分式",
            "content": "$a_n = \\dfrac{A}{3^{n-1}(2n-1)} + \\dfrac{B}{3^n(2n+1)}$。\n\n乘 $3^n(2n-1)(2n+1)$：$n+1 = 3A(2n+1) + B(2n-1) = (6A + 2B)n + (3A - B)$。\n\n$6A + 2B = 1, 3A - B = 1 \\Rightarrow A = 1/4, B = -1/4$。$\\fbox{F}=1, \\fbox{G}=4, \\fbox{HI}=-1, \\fbox{J}=4$。\n\n$S_n = \\dfrac{1}{4}\\sum(c_{k-1} - c_k) = \\dfrac{1}{4}(c_0 - c_n)$，$c_0 = 1$。$\\fbox{K}=1, \\fbox{L}=4, \\fbox{M}=1$。\n\n$\\lim c_n = 0$，故 $\\sum a_n = 1/4$。$\\fbox{N}=1, \\fbox{O}=4$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "AB=28, CD=45, E=3, FG=14, HIJ=-14, KLM=141, NO=14"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-II-2",
      "number": "II-2",
      "topic": "圆的切线与切线垂直",
      "topicTag": "解析几何",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "圆 $C$：中心 $(5, 0)$，半径 $4$。\n\n(1) $P(p, q)$ 在 $C$ 上：$p^2 - \\fbox{PQ}\\,p + q^2 + \\fbox{R} = 0$。\n切线方程：$(p - \\fbox{S})x + qy = \\fbox{T}\\,p - \\fbox{U}$。\n\n(2) $A(0, a)$（$a \\ge 0$），$AP$ 最小在 $a = \\fbox{V}$，长 $\\fbox{W}$。\n\n两条切线垂直时 $AP = \\fbox{X}$，$a = \\sqrt{\\fbox{Y}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "(1) 圆方程展开；切线方程 $(x_0 - 5)(x - 5) + y_0 y = 16$；(2) $AP^2 = AC^2 - r^2$。",
        "analysis": "两切线垂直 $\\Rightarrow$ 四边形 $APCP'$ 为正方形（$P, P'$ 切点）。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 圆方程与切线",
            "content": "$(p-5)^2 + q^2 = 16 \\Rightarrow p^2 - 10p + 25 + q^2 = 16 \\Rightarrow p^2 - 10p + q^2 + 9 = 0$。$\\fbox{PQ}=10, \\fbox{R}=9$。\n\n切线：$(p-5)(x-5) + q\\cdot y = 16 \\Rightarrow (p-5)x + qy = 16 + 5(p-5) = 5p - 9$。$\\fbox{S}=5, \\fbox{T}=5, \\fbox{U}=9$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) AP 最小与垂直",
            "content": "$A(0, a)$，$C(5,0)$，$AC^2 = 25 + a^2$。$AP^2 = AC^2 - r^2 = 25 + a^2 - 16 = 9 + a^2$。\n\n$a \\ge 0$ 时 $AP$ 在 $a = 0$ 取最小 $3$。$\\fbox{V}=0, \\fbox{W}=3$。\n\n两切线垂直 $\\Rightarrow \\angle PAP' = 90°$，结合 $\\angle APC = \\angle AP'C = 90°$ 得 $APCP'$ 是边长 $r=4$ 的正方形，故 $AP = 4$。$\\fbox{X}=4$。\n\n$AC^2 = 32 \\Rightarrow 25 + a^2 = 32 \\Rightarrow a^2 = 7 \\Rightarrow a = \\sqrt 7$。$\\fbox{Y}=7$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "PQR=109, STU=559, V=0, W=3, X=4, Y=7"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-III-1",
      "number": "III",
      "topic": "三次函数极值与区间最小值",
      "topicTag": "三次函数·微分",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$f(x) = x^3 - 3ax^2 - 3(2a+1)x + a + 2$。\n\n(1) $f'(x) = \\fbox{A}(x - \\fbox{B}\\,a - \\fbox{C})(x + \\fbox{D})$。\n(i) $a > \\fbox{EF}$：$x = -\\fbox{D}$ 时 $\\fbox{G}$；$x = \\fbox{B}\\,a + \\fbox{C}$ 时 $\\fbox{H}$。\n(ii) $a = \\fbox{EF}$：$f(x)$ 始终 $\\fbox{I}$。\n(iii) $a < \\fbox{EF}$：$x = -\\fbox{D}$ 时 $\\fbox{J}$；$x = \\fbox{B}\\,a + \\fbox{C}$ 时 $\\fbox{K}$。\n选项：⓪ 极大 ① 极小 ② 增加 ③ 减少 ④ 最大 ⑤ 最小\n\n(2) $-1 \\le x \\le 1$ 上 $f(x)$ 的最小值 $m$：\n(i) $a \\ge \\fbox{L}$：$m = \\fbox{MN}\\,a$。\n(ii) $\\fbox{OP} \\le a < \\fbox{L}$：$m = \\fbox{QR}(a^3 + \\fbox{S}\\,a^2 + \\fbox{T}\\,a)$。\n(iii) $a < \\fbox{OP}$：$m = \\fbox{U}\\,a + \\fbox{V}$。\n\n(3) (2) 的 $m$ 最大在 $a = \\dfrac{-\\fbox{W} + \\sqrt{\\fbox{X}}}{\\fbox{Y}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "$f'(x) = 3x^2 - 6ax - 3(2a+1) = 3(x - (2a+1))(x + 1)$。",
        "analysis": "临界点 $x = -1, x = 2a+1$。$[-1, 1]$ 上分三种情况看 $2a+1$ 位置。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 导数与极值",
            "content": "$f'(x) = 3x^2 - 6ax - 3(2a+1) = 3[(x+1)(x - (2a+1))]$（因为 $(x+1)(x-(2a+1)) = x^2 - 2ax - (2a+1)$）。$\\fbox{A}=3, \\fbox{B}=2, \\fbox{C}=1, \\fbox{D}=1$。\n\n(i) $a > -1$：$2a+1 > -1$ 两个不同根，开口向上 $f'$ 在 $x=-1$ 处 $f$ 取极大、$x=2a+1$ 处取极小。$\\fbox{EF}=-1, \\fbox{G}=⓪(极大), \\fbox{H}=①(极小)$。\n\n(ii) $a = -1$：$f'(x) = 3(x+1)^2 \\ge 0$，$f$ 始终增加。$\\fbox{I}=②(増加)$。\n\n(iii) $a < -1$：$2a+1 < -1$，$x = 2a+1$ 是较小根（极大），$x = -1$ 是较大根（极小）。$\\fbox{J}=⓪(極大), \\fbox{K}=①(極小)$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 区间 $[-1, 1]$ 上最小值",
            "content": "**$a \\ge 0$**：$2a+1 \\ge 1$ 在区间右外，$f$ 在 $[-1, 1]$ 递减。$f(1) = 1 - 3a - 3(2a+1) + a + 2 = -8a$。$\\fbox{L}=0, \\fbox{MN}=-8$。\n\n**$-1 \\le a < 0$**：$2a+1 \\in [-1, 1)$，$f$ 在 $x = 2a+1$ 取最小。$f(2a+1) = (2a+1)^2[(2a+1) - 3a - 3] + (a+2) = -(a+2)(2a+1)^2 + (a+2) = (a+2)[1 - (2a+1)^2] = -4a(a+1)(a+2) = -4(a^3 + 3a^2 + 2a)$。$\\fbox{OP}=-1, \\fbox{QR}=-4, \\fbox{S}=3, \\fbox{T}=2$。\n\n**$a < -1$**：$2a+1 < -1$ 在区间左外，$f$ 在 $[-1, 1]$ 递增。$f(-1) = 4a + 4$。$\\fbox{U}=4, \\fbox{V}=4$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) $m$ 最大",
            "content": "(i) $a \\ge 0$：$m = -8a$ 减，最大 $m(0) = 0$。\n(iii) $a < -1$：$m = 4a+4$ 增，最大 $m \\to 0$。\n(ii) $-1 \\le a < 0$：$m(a) = -4a(a+1)(a+2)$，$m'(a) = -4(3a^2 + 6a + 2)$。\n\n$3a^2 + 6a + 2 = 0 \\Rightarrow a = \\dfrac{-3 \\pm \\sqrt 3}{3}$。在 $(-1, 0)$ 内取 $a = \\dfrac{-3 + \\sqrt 3}{3} \\approx -0.423$，对应 $m > 0$，超过其他情形。\n\n$\\fbox{W}=3, \\fbox{X}=3, \\fbox{Y}=3$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "ABCD=3211, EF=-1, G=0, H=1, I=2, J=0, K=1, L=0, MN=-8, OP=-1, QRST=-432, UV=44, WXY=333"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c2-IV-1",
      "number": "IV",
      "topic": "对数函数切线与面积",
      "topicTag": "对数·积分",
      "humanVerified": false,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": true,
      "japanese": "$y = x\\log ax$（①），$y = 2x - 3$（②），$a > 0$。\n\n(1) ① 在 $(t, t\\log at)$ 的切线为 $\\fbox{A}$。\n选项：⓪ $y = (\\log at + 1)x - t$ ① $y = (\\log at + a)x - t$ ② $y = (a\\log t + 1)x + t$ ③ $y = (a\\log t + a)x + t$\n\n① 与 ② 相切时 $a = \\dfrac{e}{\\fbox{B}}$，切点 $(\\fbox{C}, \\fbox{D})$。\n\n(2) $a = e/\\fbox{B}$ 时 ① 在 $x = \\fbox{E}\\,e^{-\\fbox{F}}$ 处取最小值 $-\\fbox{G}\\,e^{-\\fbox{H}}$。\n\n(3) $\\int x\\log ax\\,dx = \\fbox{I} + C$。\n选项：⓪ $\\frac{1}{2}x^2\\log ax - \\frac{1}{2}x^2$ ① $2x^2\\log ax - 2x^2$ ② $\\frac{1}{2}x^2\\log ax - \\frac{1}{4}x^2$ ③ $2x^2\\log ax - 4x^2$\n\n①、②、$x$ 轴所围面积 $S = \\dfrac{\\fbox{J}}{\\fbox{K}}e^{-\\fbox{L}}$。",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "(1) $y' = \\log ax + 1$；(2) $y' = 0$；(3) 分部积分求原函数。",
        "analysis": "切线点 $(t, t\\log at)$，斜率 $\\log at + 1$。与 $y = 2x - 3$ 相切：斜率与截距均匹配。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 切线",
            "content": "$y' = \\log(ax) + 1$。切线 $y - t\\log at = (\\log at + 1)(x - t)$，化简 $y = (\\log at + 1)x - t$。$\\fbox{A}=⓪$。\n\n与 $y = 2x - 3$ 相切：斜率 $\\log at + 1 = 2 \\Rightarrow at = e$；截距 $-t = -3 \\Rightarrow t = 3$。故 $a = e/3$，切点 $(3, 3)$。$\\fbox{B}=3, \\fbox{C}=3, \\fbox{D}=3$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) ① 最小值",
            "content": "$y = x\\log(ex/3)$，$y' = \\log(ex/3) + 1 = 0 \\Rightarrow ex/3 = e^{-1} \\Rightarrow x = 3e^{-2}$。$\\fbox{E}=3, \\fbox{F}=2$。\n\n$y(3e^{-2}) = 3e^{-2}\\log(e^{-1}) = -3e^{-2}$。$\\fbox{G}=3, \\fbox{H}=2$。"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 面积",
            "content": "分部积分 $u = \\log ax, dv = x\\,dx$：$\\int x\\log ax\\,dx = (x^2/2)\\log ax - x^2/4 + C$。$\\fbox{I}=②$。\n\n曲线 ① 零点 $x = 3/e$，线 ② 零点 $x = 3/2$，切点 $(3, 3)$。\n\n令 $F(x) = (x^2/2)\\log(ex/3) - x^2/4$。$F(3) = 9/4, F(3/e) = -9/(4e^2)$。\n\n$\\int_{3/e}^{3}$ 曲线 $= 9/4 + 9/(4e^2)$；$\\int_{3/2}^{3}(2x-3)dx = 9/4$。\n\n$S = (9/4)(1 + e^{-2}) - 9/4 = (9/4)e^{-2}$。$\\fbox{J}=9, \\fbox{K}=4, \\fbox{L}=2$。"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "A=0, B=3, CD=33, EF=32, GH=32, I=2, JKL=942"
      }
    }
  ]
}
